|accessdate=2007-06-30}}</ref>
Nina Reiser obtained a temporary [[restraining order]] against Hans in December 2004 after he allegedly pushed her, at the height of the divorce proceedings.<ref name="sfgate20060914">
{{cite news
|author=Lee, Henry K.
|coauthors=Zamora, Jim Herron
